Name: Plowshare
Textual_Description: Lovingly referred to as a 'large brick with engines and guns', the Plowshare is a top of the line Purist cargo shuttle, far more spacious than the aged LIHW Llama, and easier to obtain for private use than the Merchant Reindeer. Much of the non-Merchant's Guild traffic within Purist friendly systems occurs via Plowshares.
